  <brief_title>Study to Examine the Effects of MultiStem in Ischemic Stroke</brief_title>
  <official_title>Double-Blind, Randomized, Placebo-Controlled Phase 2 Safety and Efficacy Trial of MultiStemÂ® in Adults With Ischemic Stroke</official_title>
